title: Full Show (Eagles 8-0 for first time in franchise history, Lakers win again, Can Brady and Bucs end losing streak?)
description:
00:00 Kyrie Irving suspended by the Nets
24:13 Eagles beat Texans 29-17 on TNF. Is Jalen Hurts an MVP frontrunner?
52:20 Retired NFL player Cole Beasley defends Kyrie Irving on Twitter
1:04:53 Russell Westbrook sits out final three minutes of Lakers latest win in new role with team
1:20:04 Eagles and Jalen Hurts are 8-0 for first time in franchise history
1:30:56 KD comments on Kyrie's situation
1:42:08 Can Brady and Bucs end three game losing streak agains the LA Rams?
1:48:27 Eagles fans chanted "Dallas sucks" at the end of TNF
1:53:57 Can LeBron and the Lakers earn a third straight win tonight over the Jazz?
